        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Macro- and micro-morphology of Chrysosplenium spp. A C. sangzhiense, habit (A 1), inflorescence with flowers (A 2), scanning electron micrograph (SEM) of seed 200 x (A 3), 1,000 x (A 4) B C. grayanum, habit (B 1), inflorescence with flowers (B 2), SEM of seed 150 x (B 3), 1,000 x (B 4) C C. nepalense, habit (C 1), inflorescence with flowers (C 2), SEM of seed 150 x (C 3), 1,000 x (C 4) D C. sinicum habit (D 1), inflorescence with flowers (D 2) SEM of seed 150 x (D 3), 1,000 x (D 4) (Photos by Hong Liu)." , "Figure 4. Plate of Chrysosplenium sangzhiense Hong Liu, sp. nov. A habitat B habit in flowering phase C habit in non-flowering phase D flowering stem E inflorescence with flowers (Photos by Hong Liu)." , "Figure 3. Illustration of Chrysosplenium sangzhiense Hong Liu, sp. nov. A habit in flowering phase B non-flowering stem C inflorescence with flowers D flower E capsule F seeds." ;
